npm install @angular/cli@16.0.0

to create a new application => ng new --app-name  --no-standalone
to run => npm start

to create a component => ng generate component -commponent--name


data interpolation => {{...}}
------------------

attribute binding/interpolation => [--attribute-name]='-value' , evaluation of expressions
------------------------------

binding using function => "--function_name(parameter)"
----------------------

directives: ngClass, *ngIf, *ngFor
-----------

        structural(*):
        ------------   directives that change the structure of html document through add/remove of html elements   

        


Angular Forms:
--------------

-> Template driven forms => HTML templates, simple

-> Reactive forms => Javascript/Typescript, complex


